EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Samantha.Womack.and.Rita.Simons


Celebrate 30 years of EastEnders in the company of those who know it best - the stars! Relive iconic moments and find out the real gossip from the set.

Samantha & Rita welcome you into their Walford home to celebrate 30 years of EastEnders. Re-watch classic Mitchell moments with the ladies who know them best!
